                "invention-title": [
                    "Evaporation heat transfer methanol reforming hydrogen production reactor, fuel cell and methanol reforming hydrogen production method",
                    "蒸发传热甲醇重整制氢反应器、燃料电池及甲醇重整制氢方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses an evaporation heat transfer methanol reforming hydrogen production reactor, a fuel cell and a methanol reforming hydrogen production method, and belongs to the technical field of methanol reforming hydrogen production, the reactor provided by the invention comprises a catalyst cavity and a heat transfer cavity arranged below the catalyst cavity, the catalyst cavity is filled with a catalyst for methanol reforming reaction, and the heat transfer cavity is arranged below the catalyst cavity. The reactor further comprises a heat source for providing heat; wherein a heat transfer medium layer is arranged in the heat transfer cavity, the heat transfer medium layer is gasified by the heat of the heat source to the catalyst cavity to be condensed and then returns to the bottom of the heat transfer cavity, and the whole heat transfer circulation is formed. According to the invention, the heat transfer problem of a catalyst bed is optimized, an evaporation heat exchange form is adopted, a medium is heated and gasified by using a heat source, and the gasified medium is subjected to an endothermic reaction and then condensed into a liquid state, so that the purpose of heat transfer is achieved, the overall heat transfer effect of the reactor is ensured, and the reaction rate of hydrogen production by methanol reforming is greatly improved; and the product components are optimized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请公开了一种蒸发传热甲醇重整制氢反应器、燃料电池及甲醇重整制氢方法，属于甲醇重整制氢技术领域，本申请提供的反应器包括催化剂腔和设置于催化剂腔下的传热腔，所述催化剂腔内填装有催化剂用以发生甲醇重整反应，所述反应器还包括有用以提供热量的热源；其中，所述传热腔内设置有传热介质层，所述传热介质层受所述热源热量气化至催化剂腔冷凝后回到所述传热腔底部，形成整个传热循环。本申请通过对催化剂床层传热问题进行优化，采用蒸发换热的形式，利用热源将介质升温气化，气化后的介质遇到吸热反应再冷凝回液态，从而达到热量传输的目的，保证了反应器整体的传热效果，大大提高了甲醇重整制氢反应速率，优化了产物组分。"
                }
